WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.533
Hey, good morning family!

00:00:02.545 --> 00:00:04.375
We're excited to be here today.

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:06.742
We're going to do a video together.

00:00:06.742 --> 00:00:10.480
We want to talk about being thankful.

00:00:10.856 --> 00:00:19.034
It was just on my heart; the Lord told me, 'Brandon, part of the things that the people are believing for manifestation for will come out of being thankful.

00:00:19.034 --> 00:00:25.690
' This is just where we are, and this is what we practice: walking in thanksgiving.

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.200
I want to get right to the message.

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:33.824
We were just talking, and I was trying to make it a casual thing of just what we're thinking about.

00:00:33.824 --> 00:00:38.200
Megan: we're believing for Megan to be healed, for the manifestation of her complete healing.

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:44.255
We see she's starting to talk a little; words here and there.

00:00:44.255 --> 00:00:48.147
Diana's taught her how to say—what have you been teaching her?

00:00:48.147 --> 00:00:51.090
'In the name of Jesus, I am healed.

00:00:51.090 --> 00:00:54.420
' Yeah, she goes around and says that all the time.

00:00:54.420 --> 00:00:55.565
Megan says that now.

00:00:55.565 --> 00:00:58.618
She goes around the house saying, 'In the name of Jesus, I am healed.

00:00:58.618 --> 00:01:01.044
' And what was the other thing we work on?

00:01:01.044 --> 00:01:03.240
'I have the mind of Christ.

00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:10.120
' Yep, and Megan walks around—we start, and Megan finishes—'I have the mind of Christ.

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:21.390
' We're seeing the manifestations of those scriptures come to pass in her life.

00:01:21.390 --> 00:01:23.430
I'm seeing it in her behavior.

00:01:24.538 --> 00:01:29.181
I thought if we could just get a little fraction of the Word inside of her, it would change her.

00:01:33.040 --> 00:01:41.759
Diana started trying to help her, and it's been amazing to see God just take a little bit of scripture.

00:01:42.054 --> 00:01:44.619
She doesn't say the whole thing, but 'Christ, Christ.

00:01:44.619 --> 00:01:49.103
' That's how she started, just saying 'Christ, Christ.

00:01:49.103 --> 00:01:56.500
' Then I was adding a word every time and I worked with it over weeks and months.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.639
She's finally got it down now.

00:01:59.639 --> 00:02:05.010
But she got that down back: 'Christ, mind, Christ.

00:02:05.010 --> 00:02:09.250
' It's amazing; mind, Christ, mind, Christ.

00:02:16.040 --> 00:02:16.560
It's prayer coming into fruition.

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:25.840
It's amazing because, like I said, a lot of people, if you don't see your miracle manifest instantaneously, it's not a miracle for you.

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:30.325
'Well, God didn't hear me.

00:02:30.325 --> 00:02:35.640
' But sometimes miracles are gradual.

00:02:35.640 --> 00:02:43.966
Regardless of whether it's gradual and it takes years, or if it takes days, it's still a miracle.

00:02:44.480 --> 00:02:49.040
God is faithful, so you can't give up hope.

00:02:49.493 --> 00:02:52.050
Sometimes it takes a process.

00:02:52.340 --> 00:02:58.560
I believe with all my heart she's healed now, manifestation now, but we're walking it out.

00:03:00.225 --> 00:03:01.580
We're not giving up hope.

00:03:01.580 --> 00:03:12.239
I just wanted to encourage you all that even in our life, you might think, 'These people have their stuff all together and they're spiritually so strong.

00:03:12.239 --> 00:03:16.000
' We're a work in progress just like you all.

00:03:17.575 --> 00:03:30.239
We have a special needs child, and she's been potty trained now—we're grateful—and the Lord is working a miracle in her.

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:31.860
It's been a process.

00:03:31.860 --> 00:03:37.426
I believe in God she's going to wake up tomorrow and she's going to talk in full sentences, come on here and tell you all her testimony.

00:03:37.426 --> 00:03:40.297
But right now we're taking baby steps.

00:03:41.103 --> 00:03:42.080
We're excited.

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:45.333
We have the mind of Christ.

00:03:45.333 --> 00:03:54.210
Diana's more working in it, and so we just want to encourage you all today with that miracle.

00:03:54.210 --> 00:04:01.333
Because where she was, folks—I'm telling you—they said she would never talk, she would never have a normal life; they gave up on her.

00:04:01.333 --> 00:04:06.959
Every little thing we rejoice on; we give God all the glory and all the praise.

00:04:06.959 --> 00:04:18.171
It's the biggest deal, even small, tiny things, because that's how you get to the big things: a bunch of little baby steps makes big progress.

00:04:18.503 --> 00:04:24.479
And being thankful for the small things—don't just go, 'Whatever, it's just a small thing.

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:32.795
' Like one time I was riding with somebody and the lady at the cash register handed them a free cup of coffee.

00:04:33.137 --> 00:04:37.440
I went, 'Praise God, you just got blessed with a free cup of coffee!

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:41.466
' And the person said to me, 'Oh, I don't sweat the small things.

00:04:41.466 --> 00:04:44.879
' I went, 'Hold on a minute.

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:51.160
If you don't rejoice over the small things, you won't rejoice over the big things either.

00:04:51.160 --> 00:04:54.858
' You've got to grasp a hold of even a small cup of coffee.

00:04:54.858 --> 00:05:00.453
You've got to get excited when God blesses you with five cents.

00:05:00.707 --> 00:05:06.006
You can't say, 'I'll be excited when I get a million dollars.

00:05:06.006 --> 00:05:13.268
' If you can't get excited over the dollar—come on, folks—we've got to be grateful for everything.

00:05:13.268 --> 00:05:21.280
And that's what I'm trying to get across: it's being grateful.

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:30.435
I have to go back to even when I was telling you I'm believing for a house, believing for this, believing for that—being thankful for what He's already given you.

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:44.639
There are times I murmur and complain in my heart and I get upset about things; you murmur and complain, you whine about it, and I have to stop.

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:46.010
'Father, just thank You.

00:05:46.010 --> 00:05:48.815
Thank You that today we had a meal.

00:05:49.170 --> 00:05:53.835
Thank You, Father, that You provided lights for my home.

00:05:53.835 --> 00:05:55.986
Thank You, Lord, that I have a YouTube channel.

00:05:55.986 --> 00:06:00.168
Thank You, Father, that these people even come on here and even want to listen to me.

00:06:00.168 --> 00:06:02.950
' It's humbling.

00:06:02.950 --> 00:06:06.080
'Lord, thank You for all the kind words they give me.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:10.800
I know, Lord, it's not me, it's all You, and I give You all the glory for it.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:15.560
' But they tune in, and I'm thankful for every single one of them.

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:19.800
It's very interesting just taking and being grateful for the small things.

00:06:21.387 --> 00:06:27.830
You may think, 'I don't have anything to be grateful for,' but you say, 'I'm thankful for the air that I breathe.

00:06:27.830 --> 00:06:30.840
I'm thankful for my sight.

00:06:30.840 --> 00:06:32.280
I'm thankful I have ears.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:40.279
' Find something in your life today to give God praise for.

00:06:50.129 --> 00:06:50.440
Be grateful that you have life, the opportunity that you woke up this morning to breathe.

00:06:54.154 --> 00:07:00.240
You may be in pain, but something might not hurt.

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:01.587
Maybe your toe doesn't hurt.

00:07:01.587 --> 00:07:07.460
'Thank You, Father, my toe doesn't hurt.

00:07:19.743 --> 00:07:20.189
It could be cut off.

00:07:20.189 --> 00:07:24.730
Thank You, I have a toe.

00:07:41.823 --> 00:07:42.095
Thank You, I have an earlobe.

00:07:44.194 --> 00:07:46.537
Thank You, Father, I have an eyebrow.

00:07:46.537 --> 00:07:56.065
' Find something to give Him praise for today regardless of how bad you think you've got it.

00:07:56.065 --> 00:08:04.506
It doesn't matter how small you think it is; it's big to God.

00:08:08.740 --> 00:08:10.1000
God's a good God and He deserves all our praise.

00:08:10.1000 --> 00:08:22.064
Even if it's for a star you find in the sky: 'God, I thank You for that star right there.

00:08:22.064 --> 00:08:25.168
Thank You, Father, for that star.

00:08:25.424 --> 00:08:29.405
I thank You for the tires on my car.

00:08:33.697 --> 00:08:36.211
I thank You for the dirt I walked on today.

00:08:36.211 --> 00:08:48.307
' If you don't have anything else to be thankful for, thank Him for something.

00:08:48.307 --> 00:08:48.920
Amen.

00:08:53.421 --> 00:08:55.950
When you start doing that, you'll start seeing miracles manifest in your life.

00:08:55.950 --> 00:09:02.653
You'll start seeing outpourings of the Spirit of God.

00:09:02.653 --> 00:09:15.560
God's looking for a heart who's perfect towards Him, and that is a grateful heart, a cheerful heart, a heart that's full of joy and thankfulness.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:21.685
It isn't easy to do it all the time.

00:09:33.987 --> 00:09:53.293
I have to catch myself and go back; I get in my prayer time and I go, 'Oh God, I'm sorry.

00:09:53.293 --> 00:10:00.040
I've been fussy today, had a bad attitude today.

00:10:05.933 --> 00:10:08.120
I shouldn't have been so ungrateful for what You have.

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:14.900
' He'll tell me, 'Brandon, really, what's your problem?

00:10:14.900 --> 00:10:24.529
' I'll say, 'Well, I'm irritated about this and this.

00:10:24.529 --> 00:10:31.536
' He says, 'But I've given you so much.

00:10:31.536 --> 00:10:33.636
I've blessed you so much.

00:10:33.636 --> 00:10:38.968
Why can't you take time to thank Me for that?

00:10:38.968 --> 00:10:39.742
' When the Lord asks you that...

00:10:39.742 --> 00:10:41.006
'God, forgive me.

00:10:41.006 --> 00:10:43.154
Forgive me, Lord.

00:10:43.154 --> 00:10:48.020
' You want to crawl underneath a rock.

00:10:48.020 --> 00:10:51.376
We all have our issues.

00:10:51.376 --> 00:10:57.324
But I'm just trying to tell y'all something that we have to do with Megan, and we're thanking Him for this.

00:10:57.324 --> 00:10:59.613
It's a big deal to us.

00:11:03.150 --> 00:11:03.505
You understand what I'm saying?

00:11:17.164 --> 00:11:17.373
You live it with me.

00:11:17.373 --> 00:11:19.119
Yeah, you're stirring me up.

00:11:19.119 --> 00:11:20.805
It's so good.

00:11:20.805 --> 00:11:23.833
It's time to be more thankful.

00:11:27.140 --> 00:11:27.495
I feel His presence.

00:11:27.495 --> 00:11:29.720
Thank You, Lord.

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:46.697
I don't want to just always come on here and preach to y'all; I just want to tell y'all—just being real—just being grateful will do a lot in your life.

00:11:46.697 --> 00:12:06.524
I know it seems like some days are really hard, but what I'm telling you right now works, for He inhabits the praise of His people, and when praises go up, blessings come down.

00:12:12.911 --> 00:12:13.133
If you take your eyes off of yourself...

00:12:13.133 --> 00:12:18.340
I even heard this when I traveled with Benny Hinn.

00:12:18.340 --> 00:12:33.813
When we'd go in the back room and we'd pray for the people in the back—if they took their eyes off of begging God...

00:12:33.813 --> 00:12:38.293
if you're begging, you're not believing.

00:12:38.293 --> 00:12:45.908
If you're begging God for your miracle, you're not believing.

00:12:45.908 --> 00:12:57.915
When you take your eyes off of yourself and you start praying for somebody else, that is usually when the manifestations start coming quickly.

00:12:57.915 --> 00:13:17.750
When you're consumed with yourself, worried about 'I'm dying, stage four cancer, I only have a couple of days to live, I've got to have a miracle right now,' He knows what you need.

00:13:17.750 --> 00:13:33.520
But when they took their focus off of their need and started focusing on praying for other people's needs, their manifestation instantaneously came.

00:13:33.520 --> 00:13:36.400
Those miracles were real.

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:44.853
When I ushered, I'm telling you, the manifestations of the glory of God...

00:13:44.853 --> 00:13:56.320
I've never felt them in a meeting like I did whenever I was with Benny Hinn.

00:13:56.320 --> 00:14:00.933
I was an anointing junkie.

00:14:00.933 --> 00:14:16.445
I met Diana at a Bible study, but we started going to Benny Hinn services and traveling when we first got married, ushering and helping out.

00:14:16.445 --> 00:14:27.640
We had our own needs, barely making it financially, but we were hungry and desperate.

00:14:28.010 --> 00:14:30.320
I learned a lot.

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:38.855
If you think you can achieve something by trying to be self-righteous—God can't stand self-righteousness.

00:14:50.430 --> 00:14:50.575
It is nasty to Him.

00:14:50.575 --> 00:15:02.760
So you've got to know that it's by grace you're saved through faith, and any miracle you ever get from God is because of His grace.

00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:09.720
His mercy is new every morning and great is His faithfulness to His children.

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:20.097
You can't achieve righteousness because He's the one that does it all; He paid the price for you.

00:15:20.097 --> 00:15:22.667
Thank You, Jesus.

00:15:33.260 --> 00:15:35.297
Don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:15:51.338 --> 00:15:51.555
He said to me, 'Son, remember the video you just did about believing Me for big things in 2024?

00:16:00.284 --> 00:16:03.076
A lot of my kids already have given up on it.

00:16:03.076 --> 00:16:11.383
You're only four weeks into the year and they've already given up on their dream.

00:16:11.383 --> 00:16:22.319
' I want you to brush it off, blow it off, dust it off—it's only four weeks old—and believe Him again.

00:16:22.319 --> 00:16:27.719
Touch that hem of His garment.

00:16:27.719 --> 00:16:35.766
Believing for your house, believing for your spouse, believing for your miracle.

00:16:35.766 --> 00:16:39.573
God has a plan for your life.

00:16:39.573 --> 00:16:47.639
Latch onto it like the woman with the issue of blood.

00:16:53.079 --> 00:16:54.909
Say, 'I'm not letting go of this until I get my miracle.

00:16:54.909 --> 00:17:02.167
' Part of it is being thankful for what you have.

00:17:02.167 --> 00:17:11.445
I felt it in my heart to finish this off today to tell you all: God loves you, and we love you.

00:17:24.959 --> 00:17:25.110
We pray for you all the time.

00:17:25.110 --> 00:17:28.285
Diana gets behind the computer and reads your emails.

00:17:29.995 --> 00:17:37.754
We take it very seriously—this gift what God's given us, our congregation.

00:17:37.754 --> 00:17:53.710
When you want to bless us with finances, we pray for your money; we pray for harvest, for abundance, for new jobs, creative ideas to get wealth.

00:18:05.040 --> 00:18:05.440
We believe in the supernatural in this household.

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:07.720
God shows up and shows off.

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:12.080
He is ruling and reigning inside of you.

00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:20.851
Good things are ahead for you if you believe.

00:18:20.851 --> 00:18:25.739
2024 will be a good year for you.

00:18:25.739 --> 00:18:28.391
What are you believing for?

00:18:28.391 --> 00:18:31.189
What are you thankful for?

00:18:31.189 --> 00:18:35.926
My wife, my kids, my health.

00:18:35.926 --> 00:18:46.145
Even when I'm overcoming something, I'm thankful, 'Father, You've healed me.

00:18:46.145 --> 00:18:52.520
' I thank You, Father, that You've set me free from obesity.

00:18:52.520 --> 00:19:00.327
Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world!

00:19:00.327 --> 00:19:05.871
Click the like button, the subscribe button, and our notification bell.

00:19:10.399 --> 00:19:10.639
It helps us get the Gospel out.

00:19:10.639 --> 00:19:12.090
It's the algorithm.

00:19:12.090 --> 00:19:20.039
When you do that, the Gospel is spreading throughout the whole world.

00:19:20.039 --> 00:19:26.029
Africa, Australia, Europe, Japan, China—this channel is touching their lives.

00:19:26.029 --> 00:19:37.240
People getting born again, people turning from homosexuality to give their heart to Jesus, wayward children coming home.

00:19:37.240 --> 00:19:41.120
People are getting healed, delivered from demonic spirits.

00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:46.919
It's because of you all clicking that like button.

00:19:46.919 --> 00:19:53.768
We don't take any one of you all for granted.

00:19:55.658 --> 00:19:55.933
God bless y'all.

00:19:55.933 --> 00:19:58.731
Let's pray real quick.

00:19:58.731 --> 00:20:09.120
'Father, we thank You for every single person who's part of this YouTube channel.

00:20:09.120 --> 00:20:21.505
Diana and I agree in the name of Jesus that they are blessed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:39.137
You said in Your Word that You'd meet all their needs, and I thank You, God, that You're a faithful God and You bring that harvest to them now.

00:20:39.137 --> 00:20:43.848
Thank You, Lord, for jobs and better jobs.

00:20:43.848 --> 00:20:52.383
Thank You, Lord, for food for their homes and for their bills being paid.

00:20:52.383 --> 00:21:06.120
But Lord, I thank You for the overflow, that they're living in abundance to the extreme, that they've got so much they're able to help the people around them.

00:21:06.120 --> 00:21:12.074
We're a funnel, a pitcher to pour out and help everybody else.

00:21:12.749 --> 00:21:14.969
Lord, I thank You for creative ideas to get wealth.

00:21:14.969 --> 00:21:18.520
But Lord, I thank You that they may need healing in their body.

00:21:18.520 --> 00:21:20.760
You paid the price for that too.

00:21:27.779 --> 00:21:30.359
By Your stripes we are healed.

00:21:30.799 --> 00:21:37.333
I speak healing and wholeness over their bodies today in the name of Jesus.

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:39.977
Throats be healed.

00:21:44.400 --> 00:21:48.187
Congestion and viruses, be gone.

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:53.154
Deliverance over their bodies.

00:21:55.760 --> 00:21:57.360
Oh, somebody needs new...

00:21:57.360 --> 00:21:58.960
I just saw it...

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:04.251
something going on with your blood.

00:22:04.251 --> 00:22:06.679
I speak healing over your blood right now.

00:22:06.999 --> 00:22:07.639
It's leukemia.

00:22:07.639 --> 00:22:08.919
The Lord said leukemia.

00:22:11.114 --> 00:22:17.515
I curse leukemia right now in the name of Jesus and we call it to go now.

00:22:22.680 --> 00:22:24.606
Healing belongs to you.

00:22:31.890 --> 00:22:34.253
You're not underneath the curse.

00:22:34.253 --> 00:22:39.089
God doesn't teach people through sickness and disease.

00:22:39.720 --> 00:22:46.384
The Bible says He comes that you might have life more abundantly.

00:22:55.340 --> 00:22:55.680
He doesn't have sickness in heaven, so He can't give it to you.

00:22:55.680 --> 00:23:00.851
The devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:23:02.610 --> 00:23:06.970
He took all infirmities so that you don't have to have them.

00:23:06.970 --> 00:23:10.400
Jesus paid it for you.

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:16.620
Sow a seed, believing for a manifestation of healing.

00:23:16.620 --> 00:23:22.279
Father, I take authority over leukemia right now.

00:23:22.279 --> 00:23:28.543
Get out of their body right now in Jesus' name.

00:23:28.543 --> 00:23:33.650
We call them healed and whole and well.

00:23:33.650 --> 00:23:40.426
Lord, anybody else that needs a miracle, You have made and paid the way.

00:23:40.426 --> 00:23:42.409
We consider it done.

00:23:42.409 --> 00:23:49.826
We call them healed from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:23:49.826 --> 00:23:53.119
God, You fixed it all.

00:23:53.119 --> 00:24:00.967
If you got a miracle today, comment down below.

00:24:00.967 --> 00:24:02.903
Tell the people.

00:24:02.903 --> 00:24:04.417
We are excited for you.

00:24:04.417 --> 00:24:06.000
Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:07.720
See you next time.

